					<img alt='' src='http://www.gravatar.com/avatar/1641f3027788df47f877f656559559f1?s=48&amp;d=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gravatar.com%2Favatar%2Fad516503a11cd5ca435acc9bb6523536%3Fs%3D48&amp;r=G' class='author-profile-pic avatar avatar-48 photo' height='48' width='48' />	
					<cite class=\"comment-author\">
						<a href='http://www.haaqi.com' rel='external nofollow' class='url'>Magic Dragon</a>					</cite>
				</div>
					
				<p>Money, capitalism the idea of profit forces companies (airlines in this case) to reduce costs and increase risks (in this case to flying passengers)!  It&#8217;s simple!</p>
	
				<div class=\"comment-meta commentmetadata\">
					<a href=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/2009/06/06/air-bus-af-447-sorrow-lack-of-information-and-sensationalism/comment-page-1/#comment-1569748\"> # </a>
