                                   'media_id' => 1,
                                   'publish_date' => '2009-06-06 16:37:36',
                                   'sentence' => "Although authorities haven\x{2019}t yet confirmed that the floating seats are indeed from the missing Air France jet, it\x{2019}s pretty easy to see on the map above that for once, this possible tragedy has nothing to do with aliens or electromagnetic fields or the ghost of Amelia Earhart.",
                                   'sentence_number' => 66,
                                   'stories_id' => 11,
                                   'story_sentences_id' => '602'
                                 },
                                 {
                                   'db_row_last_updated' => '2016-01-15 13:08:35.494431-06',
                                   'disable_triggers' => 0,
                                   'is_dup' => undef,
                                   'language' => 'en',
                                   'media_id' => 1,
                                   'publish_date' => '2009-06-06 16:37:36',
                                   'sentence' => 'It does, however, have everything to do with freak accidents and airplane safety.',
                                   'sentence_number' => 67,
                                   'stories_id' => 11,
                                   'story_sentences_id' => '603'
                                 },
                                 {
                                   'db_row_last_updated' => '2016-01-15 13:08:35.494431-06',
                                   'disable_triggers' => 0,
                                   'is_dup' => undef,
                                   'language' => 'en',
                                   'media_id' => 1,
                                   'publish_date' => '2009-06-06 16:37:36',
                                   'sentence' => "Not forgetting the Bermuda Triangle effect, Polish blog Tierra Incognita [pl], wonders what has happened, affirming that despite the catastrophe of the disappearance, he stills loves flying: Uwielbiam lata\x{107} samolotem.",
                                   'sentence_number' => 68,
                                   'stories_id' => 11,
                                   'story_sentences_id' => '604'
                                 },
                                 {
                                   'db_row_last_updated' => '2016-01-15 13:08:35.494431-06',
                                   'disable_triggers' => 0,
                                   'is_dup' => undef,
                                   'language' => 'pl',
                                   'media_id' => 1,
                                   'publish_date' => '2009-06-06 16:37:36',
                                   'sentence' => "Podr\x{f3}\x{17c} lotnicza nie wywo\x{142}uje u mnie \x{17c}adnego stresu, wr\x{119}cz przeciwnie \x{2013} dzia\x{142}a uspokajaj\x{105}co i relaksuj\x{105}co.",
                                   'sentence_number' => 69,
                                   'stories_id' => 11,
                                   'story_sentences_id' => '605'
                                 },
                                 {
                                   'db_row_last_updated' => '2016-01-15 13:08:35.494431-06',
                                   'disable_triggers' => 0,
                                   'is_dup' => undef,
                                   'language' => 'pl',
                                   'media_id' => 1,
                                   'publish_date' => '2009-06-06 16:37:36',
                                   'sentence' => "W chwili gdy maszyna odrywa si\x{119} od ziemi wpadam w specyficzny b\x{142}ogostan, mam wra\x{17c}enie \x{17c}e wszystkie moje problemy i zmartwienia pozosta\x{142}y tam na dole.",
                                   'sentence_number' => 70,
                                   'stories_id' => 11,
                                   'story_sentences_id' => '606'
                                 },
                                 {
                                   'db_row_last_updated' => '2016-01-15 13:08:35.494431-06',
                                   'disable_triggers' => 0,
                                   'is_dup' => undef,
                                   'language' => 'pl',
                                   'media_id' => 1,
                                   'publish_date' => '2009-06-06 16:37:36',
                                   'sentence' => "\x{15a}wiadomo\x{15b}\x{107}, \x{17c}e przez najbli\x{17c}sze kilka godzin podr\x{f3}\x{17c}y b\x{119}d\x{119} w zupe\x{142}nie innym wymiarze, gdzie w sumie nic ode mnie nie zale\x{17c}y, sprawia mi wielk\x{105} frajd\x{119}.",
                                   'sentence_number' => 71,
                                   'stories_id' => 11,
                                   'story_sentences_id' => '607'
                                 },
                                 {
                                   'db_row_last_updated' => '2016-01-15 13:08:35.494431-06',
                                   'disable_triggers' => 0,
                                   'is_dup' => undef,
                                   'language' => 'pl',
                                   'media_id' => 1,
                                   'publish_date' => '2009-06-06 16:37:36',
                                   'sentence' => "Jak dziecko, godzinami mog\x{119} gapi\x{107} si\x{119} przez okienko, nawet je\x{15b}li to czarna noc i wida\x{107} tylko gwiazdy.",
                                   'sentence_number' => 72,
                                   'stories_id' => 11,
                                   'story_sentences_id' => '608'
                                 },
                                 {
                                   'db_row_last_updated' => '2016-01-15 13:08:35.494431-06',
                                   'disable_triggers' => 0,
                                   'is_dup' => undef,
                                   'language' => 'pl',
                                   'media_id' => 1,
                                   'publish_date' => '2009-06-06 16:37:36',
                                   'sentence' => "Zastanawiam si\x{119} dlaczego ten w\x{142}a\x{15b}nie wypadek a\x{17c} tak bardzo wlaz\x{142} mi pod sk\x{f3}r\x{119}?",
                                   'sentence_number' => 73,
                                   'stories_id' => 11,
                                   'story_sentences_id' => '609'
                                 },
                                 {
                                   'db_row_last_updated' => '2016-01-15 13:08:35.494431-06',
                                   'disable_triggers' => 0,
                                   'is_dup' => undef,
                                   'language' => 'pl',
                                   'media_id' => 1,
                                   'publish_date' => '2009-06-06 16:37:36',
                                   'sentence' => "Z\x{142}o\x{17c}y\x{142}o si\x{119} na to pewnie kilka czynnik\x{f3}w \x{2013} Air France jest jednym z moich ulubionych przewo\x{17a}nik\x{f3}w, dos\x{142}ownie kilkana\x{15b}cie dni temu odprowadza\x{142}em blisk\x{105} przyjaci\x{f3}\x{142}k\x{119} na samolot lec\x{105}cy z Caracas do Pary\x{17c}a, a ja sam te\x{17c} na trasie Ameryka Po\x{142}udniowa \x{2013} Europa latam do\x{15b}\x{107} cz\x{119}sto.",
                                   'sentence_number' => 74,
                                   'stories_id' => 11,
                                   'story_sentences_id' => '610'
                                 },
                                 {
                                   'db_row_last_updated' => '2016-01-15 13:08:35.494431-06',
                                   'disable_triggers' => 0,
                                   'is_dup' => undef,
                                   'language' => 'pl',
                                   'media_id' => 1,
                                   'publish_date' => '2009-06-06 16:37:36',
                                   'sentence' => "No i jeszcze ta tajemniczo\x{15b}\x{107} tej katastrofy \x{2013} nie \x{17c}adne \x{201e}tradycyjne\x{201d} k\x{142}opoty przy starcie, b\x{105}d\x{17a} l\x{105}dowaniu, ale zagini\x{119}cie gdzie\x{15b} na \x{15b}rodku oceanu.",
                                   'sentence_number' => 75,
                                   'stories_id' => 11,
                                   'story_sentences_id' => '611'
                                 },
                                 {
                                   'db_row_last_updated' => '2016-01-15 13:08:35.494431-06',
                                   'disable_triggers' => 0,
                                   'is_dup' => undef,
                                   'language' => 'pl',
                                   'media_id' => 1,
                                   'publish_date' => '2009-06-06 16:37:36',
                                   'sentence' => "Dobrze, \x{17c}e przynajmniej nie nad Tr\x{f3}jk\x{105}tem Bermudzkim...",
                                   'sentence_number' => 76,
                                   'stories_id' => 11,
                                   'story_sentences_id' => '612'
                                 },
                                 {
                                   'db_row_last_updated' => '2016-01-15 13:08:35.494431-06',
                                   'disable_triggers' => 0,
                                   'is_dup' => undef,
                                   'language' => 'pl',
                                   'media_id' => 1,
                                   'publish_date' => '2009-06-06 16:37:36',
                                   'sentence' => "Na szcz\x{119}\x{15b}cie nie s\x{105}dz\x{119} aby ten wypadek zmieni\x{142} m\x{f3}j stosunek do latania.",
                                   'sentence_number' => 77,
                                   'stories_id' => 11,
                                   'story_sentences_id' => '613'
                                 },
                                 {
                                   'db_row_last_updated' => '2016-01-15 13:08:35.494431-06',
                                   'disable_triggers' => 0,
                                   'is_dup' => undef,
                                   'language' => 'pl',
                                   'media_id' => 1,
                                   'publish_date' => '2009-06-06 16:37:36',
                                   'sentence' => "Nadal si\x{119} ciesz\x{119}, \x{17c}e prawdopodobnie jeszcze w tym miesi\x{105}cu b\x{119}d\x{119} musia\x{142} kilka razy wsi\x{105}\x{15b}\x{107} do samolotu.",
                                   'sentence_number' => 78,
                                   'stories_id' => 11,
                                   'story_sentences_id' => '614'
                                 },
                                 {
                                   'db_row_last_updated' => '2016-01-15 13:08:35.494431-06',
                                   'disable_triggers' => 0,
                                   'is_dup' => undef,
                                   'language' => 'pl',
                                   'media_id' => 1,
                                   'publish_date' => '2009-06-06 16:37:36',
                                   'sentence' => "I wci\x{105}\x{17c} mam nadziej\x{119}, \x{17c}e jeszcze w tym roku uda mi si\x{119} dolecie\x{107} samolotem do Ksi\x{119}\x{17c}yca...",
                                   'sentence_number' => 79,
                                   'stories_id' => 11,
                                   'story_sentences_id' => '615'
                                 },
                                 {
                                   'db_row_last_updated' => '2016-01-15 13:08:35.494431-06',
                                   'disable_triggers' => 0,
                                   'is_dup' => undef,
                                   'language' => 'en',
                                   'media_id' => 1,
                                   'publish_date' => '2009-06-06 16:37:36',
                                   'sentence' => 'I love flying on air planes.',
                                   'sentence_number' => 80,
                                   'stories_id' => 11,
                                   'story_sentences_id' => '616'
                                 },
                                 {
                                   'db_row_last_updated' => '2016-01-15 13:08:35.494431-06',
                                   'disable_triggers' => 0,
                                   'is_dup' => undef,
                                   'language' => 'en',
                                   'media_id' => 1,
                                   'publish_date' => '2009-06-06 16:37:36',
                                   'sentence' => 'The air travel is not stressful to me at all, on the contrary - it relaxes me and calms me down.',
                                   'sentence_number' => 81,
                                   'stories_id' => 11,
                                   'story_sentences_id' => '617'
                                 },
                                 {
                                   'db_row_last_updated' => '2016-01-15 13:08:35.494431-06',
                                   'disable_triggers' => 0,
                                   'is_dup' => undef,
                                   'language' => 'en',
                                   'media_id' => 1,
                                   'publish_date' => '2009-06-06 16:37:36',
                                   'sentence' => 'The moment the machine stops touching earth I get into a specific state of peacefulness, I have a feeling that all my problems and troubles are left below.',
                                   'sentence_number' => 82,
                                   'stories_id' => 11,
                                   'story_sentences_id' => '618'
                                 },
                                 {
                                   'db_row_last_updated' => '2016-01-15 13:08:35.494431-06',
                                   'disable_triggers' => 0,
                                   'is_dup' => undef,
                                   'language' => 'en',
                                   'media_id' => 1,
                                   'publish_date' => '2009-06-06 16:37:36',
                                   'sentence' => 'The thought of being stuck for the next few hours in a completely different dimention where nothing really depends on me, is really cool.',
                                   'sentence_number' => 83,
                                   'stories_id' => 11,
                                   'story_sentences_id' => '619'
                                 },
                                 {
                                   'db_row_last_updated' => '2016-01-15 13:08:35.494431-06',
                                   'disable_triggers' => 0,
                                   'is_dup' => undef,
                                   'language' => 'en',
                                   'media_id' => 1,
                                   'publish_date' => '2009-06-06 16:37:36',
                                   'sentence' => 'Like a kid, I can stare through the window for hours, even if its nighttime and all I can see is stars.',
                                   'sentence_number' => 84,
                                   'stories_id' => 11,
                                   'story_sentences_id' => '620'
                                 },
                                 {
                                   'db_row_last_updated' => '2016-01-15 13:08:35.494431-06',
                                   'disable_triggers' => 0,
                                   'is_dup' => undef,
                                   'language' => 'en',
                                   'media_id' => 1,
                                   'publish_date' => '2009-06-06 16:37:36',
                                   'sentence' => 'I wonder why exactly this accident touched me so deeply?',
                                   'sentence_number' => 85,
                                   'stories_id' => 11,
                                   'story_sentences_id' => '621'
                                 },
                                 {
                                   'db_row_last_updated' => '2016-01-15 13:08:35.494431-06',
                                   'disable_triggers' => 0,
                                   'is_dup' => undef,
                                   'language' => 'en',
                                   'media_id' => 1,
                                   'publish_date' => '2009-06-06 16:37:36',
                                   'sentence' => 'Probably there are a few reasons - Air France is one of my favourite companies, just a few days ago I walked my close friend for a flight from Caracas to Paris, and I myself very often travel on the line South America - Europe.',
                                   'sentence_number' => 86,
                                   'stories_id' => 11,
                                   'story_sentences_id' => '622'
                                 },
                                 {
                                   'db_row_last_updated' => '2016-01-15 13:08:35.494431-06',
                                   'disable_triggers' => 0,
                                   'is_dup' => undef,
                                   'language' => 'en',
                                   'media_id' => 1,
                                   'publish_date' => '2009-06-06 16:37:36',
                                   'sentence' => "And the whole mystery surrounding this catastrophe \x{2013} not the \x{2018}usual' problems with take off or landing, but disappearance somewhere in the middle of the ocean.",
                                   'sentence_number' => 87,
                                   'stories_id' => 11,
                                   'story_sentences_id' => '623'
                                 },
                                 {
                                   'db_row_last_updated' => '2016-01-15 13:08:35.494431-06',
                                   'disable_triggers' => 0,
                                   'is_dup' => undef,
                                   'language' => 'en',
                                   'media_id' => 1,
                                   'publish_date' => '2009-06-06 16:37:36',
                                   'sentence' => 'Good job it didn\'t happen over the Bermuda Triangle...',
                                   'sentence_number' => 88,
                                   'stories_id' => 11,
                                   'story_sentences_id' => '624'
                                 },
                                 {
                                   'db_row_last_updated' => '2016-01-15 13:08:35.494431-06',
                                   'disable_triggers' => 0,
                                   'is_dup' => undef,
                                   'language' => 'en',
                                   'media_id' => 1,
                                   'publish_date' => '2009-06-06 16:37:36',
                                   'sentence' => 'Luckily I do not think that this accident will change my attitude towards flying.',
                                   'sentence_number' => 89,
                                   'stories_id' => 11,
                                   'story_sentences_id' => '625'
                                 },
                                 {
                                   'db_row_last_updated' => '2016-01-15 13:08:35.494431-06',
                                   'disable_triggers' => 0,
                                   'is_dup' => undef,
                                   'language' => 'en',
                                   'media_id' => 1,
                                   'publish_date' => '2009-06-06 16:37:36',
                                   'sentence' => 'I am still happy that I will most probably have to sit on a plane a few times this month.',
                                   'sentence_number' => 90,
                                   'stories_id' => 11,
                                   'story_sentences_id' => '626'
                                 },
                                 {
                                   'db_row_last_updated' => '2016-01-15 13:08:35.494431-06',
                                   'disable_triggers' => 0,
                                   'is_dup' => undef,
                                   'language' => 'en',
                                   'media_id' => 1,
                                   'publish_date' => '2009-06-06 16:37:36',
                                   'sentence' => 'And I hope that this month too I will be able to catch the plane to the Moon.',
                                   'sentence_number' => 91,
                                   'stories_id' => 11,
                                   'story_sentences_id' => '627'
                                 },
                                 {
                                   'db_row_last_updated' => '2016-01-15 13:08:35.494431-06',
                                   'disable_triggers' => 0,
                                   'is_dup' => undef,
                                   'language' => 'en',
                                   'media_id' => 1,
                                   'publish_date' => '2009-06-06 16:37:36',
                                   'sentence' => 'Discussions and rumours have begun to focus not only on the strange weather patterns in the part of the Atlantic where the plane went down, but also on the computer systems on the Airbus A330-203.',
                                   'sentence_number' => 92,
                                   'stories_id' => 11,
                                   'story_sentences_id' => '628'
                                 },
                                 {
                                   'db_row_last_updated' => '2016-01-15 13:08:35.494431-06',
                                   'disable_triggers' => 0,
                                   'is_dup' => undef,
                                   'language' => 'en',
                                   'media_id' => 1,
                                   'publish_date' => '2009-06-06 16:37:36',
                                   'sentence' => 'Specifically, some are investigating the coincidences between the Air France flight and an October 2008 Quantas flight headed for Perth, Australia that dropped 200 meters in a matter of minutes, forcing the plane to make an emergency landing.',
                                   'sentence_number' => 93,
                                   'stories_id' => 11,
                                   'story_sentences_id' => '629'
                                 },
                                 {
                                   'db_row_last_updated' => '2016-01-15 13:08:35.494431-06',
                                   'disable_triggers' => 0,
                                   'is_dup' => undef,
                                   'language' => 'en',
                                   'media_id' => 1,
                                   'publish_date' => '2009-06-06 16:37:36',
                                   'sentence' => 'Others argue this incident is not relevant to the recent disaster.',
                                   'sentence_number' => 94,
                                   'stories_id' => 11,
                                   'story_sentences_id' => '630'
                                 },
                                 {
                                   'db_row_last_updated' => '2016-01-15 13:08:35.494431-06',
                                   'disable_triggers' => 0,
                                   'is_dup' => undef,
                                   'language' => 'en',
                                   'media_id' => 1,
                                   'publish_date' => '2009-06-06 16:37:36',
                                   'sentence' => 'From Plane Talking , written by Ben Sandilands at Crikey Blogs in Australia.',
                                   'sentence_number' => 95,
                                   'stories_id' => 11,
                                   'story_sentences_id' => '631'
                                 },
                                 {
                                   'db_row_last_updated' => '2016-01-15 13:08:35.494431-06',
                                   'disable_triggers' => 0,
                                   'is_dup' => undef,
                                   'language' => 'en',
                                   'media_id' => 1,
                                   'publish_date' => '2009-06-06 16:37:36',
                                   'sentence' => 'It has been reported by The Aviation Herald, an online Europe based journal of aviation incidents and news that the main body of electronic alerts begin with the disengagement of the autopilot and were followed by messages related to the ADIRU or air data and inertial reference units and the PRIM or flight control primary computer which is informed about speed, attitude and other material flight values by the ADIRUs.',
                                   'sentence_number' => 96,
                                   'stories_id' => 11,
                                   'story_sentences_id' => '632'
                                 },
                                 {
                                   'db_row_last_updated' => '2016-01-15 13:08:35.494431-06',
                                   'disable_triggers' => 0,
                                   'is_dup' => undef,
                                   'language' => 'en',
                                   'media_id' => 1,
                                   'publish_date' => '2009-06-06 16:37:36',
                                   'sentence' => 'Superficially this resembles the onset of the mid air upset that caused Qantas flight QF72 from Singapore to Perth to make an emergency landing in Learmonth last October.',
                                   'sentence_number' => 97,
                                   'stories_id' => 11,
                                   'story_sentences_id' => '633'
                                 },
                                 {
                                   'db_row_last_updated' => '2016-01-15 13:08:35.494431-06',
                                   'disable_triggers' => 0,
                                   'is_dup' => undef,
                                   'language' => 'en',
                                   'media_id' => 1,
                                   'publish_date' => '2009-06-06 16:37:36',
                                   'sentence' => 'The PRIM will in some flight modes intervene in the flight controls settings of the jet to inhibit pilot inputs which would exceed critical limits which could stall the airliner, or overload parts of the structure or control surfaces on the wings or rudder.',
                                   'sentence_number' => 98,
                                   'stories_id' => 11,
                                   'story_sentences_id' => '634'
                                 },
                                 {
                                   'db_row_last_updated' => '2016-01-15 13:08:35.494431-06',
                                   'disable_triggers' => 0,
                                   'is_dup' => undef,
                                   'language' => 'en',
                                   'media_id' => 1,
                                   'publish_date' => '2009-06-06 16:37:36',
                                   'sentence' => 'However these limitations can also be in turn locked out by the pilot.',
                                   'sentence_number' => 99,
                                   'stories_id' => 11,
                                   'story_sentences_id' => '635'
                                 },
                                 {
                                   'db_row_last_updated' => '2016-01-15 13:08:35.494431-06',
                                   'disable_triggers' => 0,
                                   'is_dup' => undef,
                                   'language' => 'en',
                                   'media_id' => 1,
                                   'publish_date' => '2009-06-06 16:37:36',
                                   'sentence' => "Other reports indicate that these \x{2018}unprecedented\x{2019} messages were concentrated in a four minute period, ending with a final advisory message about the vertical speed, that is, the rate at which the jet was falling rather than any speed with which it was also moving forwards.",
                                   'sentence_number' => 100,
                                   'stories_id' => 11,
                                   'story_sentences_id' => '636'
                                 },
                                 {
                                   'db_row_last_updated' => '2016-01-15 13:08:35.494431-06',
                                   'disable_triggers' => 0,
                                   'is_dup' => undef,
                                   'language' => 'en',
                                   'media_id' => 1,
                                   'publish_date' => '2009-06-06 16:37:36',
                                   'sentence' => 'Faulty ADIRU units in the Qantas A330-300 operating the flight that diverted to Learmonth remain a major focus of an unfinished air accident investigation by the ATSB.',
                                   'sentence_number' => 101,
                                   'stories_id' => 11,
                                   'story_sentences_id' => '637'
                                 },
                                 {
                                   'db_row_last_updated' => '2016-01-15 13:08:35.494431-06',
                                   'disable_triggers' => 0,
                                   'is_dup' => undef,
                                   'language' => 'en',
                                   'media_id' => 1,
                                   'publish_date' => '2009-06-06 16:37:36',
                                   'sentence' => 'That investigation is also looking at other ADIRU related incidents on Qantas A330s.',
                                   'sentence_number' => 102,
                                   'stories_id' => 11,
                                   'story_sentences_id' => '638'
                                 },
                                 {
                                   'db_row_last_updated' => '2016-01-15 13:08:35.494431-06',
                                   'disable_triggers' => 0,
                                   'is_dup' => undef,
                                   'language' => 'en',
                                   'media_id' => 1,
                                   'publish_date' => '2009-06-06 16:37:36',
                                   'sentence' => 'However the Qantas ADIRU units were made by Northrop Grumman, while those in the Air France jet were made by Honeywell, They are two completely different designs, running totally different sets of programmed logic to serve the same ends.',
                                   'sentence_number' => 103,
                                   'stories_id' => 11,
                                   'story_sentences_id' => '639'
